org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode

Class stateslist

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.stateslist

  • class stateslist
extends java.lang.Object
    list of states for the state machine each state can be referenced in other programs for use in various autonomous programs
